 Remove authorization  API   and add a new redis entry for roles and perimissions. The structure in redis looks like this
"so write": ["SALES_MANAGER", "ADMIN" ....] 
Also, make change regarding the claims  API to add updated response mentioned below.
{
    "data": {
        "dataGroups": {
            "data-group-2": "SALES_MANAGER"
},
        "globalRoles": [
            {
                "region": "ALL",
                "role": "ADMIN"
            },
            {
                "region": "US-region-id",
                "role": "SALES_MANAGER"
            }
        ]
    }
}

Add a fab which shows Plus icon by default. Please note, the Plus would be replaced with the default Hamburger icon (3 lines) in future if user selects tasks from the list.
Create a form for task creation. You can omit fields:
Due By (time field).
Possibly, Reminder can be omitted as well if there's no data to display in a dropdown
Please use field label without a verb (use "Context" instead of "Add Context", etc).

Things to keep in mind:
There will be Edit task functionality, so let's see if we want to reuse the same form or we'll create a separate one
The same form will be used in other entity info panes later (Open Account info pane, FAB → Add Task → The form opens)


Find API contract in Swagger http://10.40.1.223:8082/?urls.primaryName=account#/Task/createTasks 
Alex used this sample JSON to create tasks, attaching for reference:
